  <p>For the broader technique sequence, use the <a href="/learn/how-to-put-on-compression-socks-easily">general compression-sock donning guide</a>, the <a href="/learn/donnease-adaptive-compression-guide">DonnEase™ adaptive compression guide</a>, and the <a href="/learn/compression-101">Compression 101 guide</a>. If your setup includes another person, use the <a href="/learn/caregiver-guide-compression-socks">caregiver guide for compression socks</a>; if your mobility-aid use is tied to SCI, read the <a href="/learn/compression-socks-spinal-cord-injury">compression socks for spinal cord injury guide</a> and consult your healthcare provider for condition-specific decisions.</p>

